data.name: plot.Text
data.value: The Good, The Bad and The Ugly is a 1966 Italian epic Spaghetti Western film directed by Sergio Leone, starring Clint Eastwood, Lee Van Cleef, and Eli Wallach in the title roles. The story takes place during the American Civil War, following a trio of bounty hunters who are on the hunt for a fortune in Confederate gold.
